<div class="container">
    <a href="/" class="back-button">
        <span>‚Üê</span> Back to Portfolio
    </a>

    <section class="category-page">
        <header class="category-header">
            <h1>üè• Healthcare & Medical Applications</h1>
            <p class="category-intro">
                AI-powered healthcare solutions including RAG chatbots for patient support, medical practice management systems, 
                and specialized applications for oncology, dental care, and mental health. These projects demonstrate real-world 
                applications of AI in regulated healthcare environments with focus on patient safety and compliance.
